Dialogue: 0,00:13:35.60,00:13:39.33,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,I can t believe she ever meant\nany harm to the People of the Sea\n我不相信她曾动过对海上一族不利的念头
Dialogue: 0,00:13:39.86,00:13:42.33,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,Something has\nhappened, I,'m sure of it\n肯定是发生什么事了
